## Modelling
# Stratefied Sampling
inTrain <- createDataPartition(y = df$imdb_score, list = FALSE, p = .8)
train <- df[inTrain,]
test <- df[-inTrain,]
stopifnot(nrow(train) + nrow(test) == nrow(df))

# We will train multiple models on 5 foldCV and 1 repeat.
# Once we get the best model we will increase the repeats to get better prediction.

execModel <- function(modelName, nfolds, nrepeat){
  trctrl <- trainControl(method = "repeatedcv", 
                         number = nfolds, 
                         repeats = nrepeat)
  
  model <- caret::train(imdb_score ~ . 
                            , data = train
                            , method = modelName
                            , metric = "RMSE"
                            , preProcess = "scale"
                            , trControl = trctrl)
  print(model$results)
  print(model$finalModel)
  return(model)
}
